text: Timothy I may refer to: * Pope Timothy I of Alexandria, Pope of Alexandria & Patriarch of the See of St. Mark in 378–384 * Timothy I of Constantinople, Patriarch of Constantinople in 511–518 * Timothy I (Nestorian patriarch), Catholicus-Patriarch of the East in 780–823 * Timotheus I of Jerusalem, patriarch in 1935–1955 * The First Epistle to Timothy
title: Timothy I
